data.description: This wonderful 3 bedroom/2bath home is located close to Gunter AFB, Eastbrook, and easy access to downtown. Original hardwood floors are in most of the home. The entire home is handicap accessible. The kitchen is extra large with an abundance of cabinetry and a sink that overlooks the large, private back yard. The family room is very spacious, has built-in bookshelves and a large picture window. The living space flows perfectly into the dining room. There is a large master suite with a sitting area, fireplace and a door that leads out to the nice patio.  The huge lot is completely fenced in and wooded - great for kids and pets! There is also a one car attached garage. This would be a wonderful investment home or great for a first-time home buyer.
